understanding of the administrations problems 
what that flap indicates is the extraordinary problems that we 
have in dealing with narcotics in the international sphere he 
says this is the most unique problem that law enforcement has 
ever dealt with 
kellner differs strongly with those who say legalization of 
drugs could solve problems stemming from the drug trade 
