the huge may decline suprised analysts who had been expecting 
only a modest decline because of rising mortgage interest rates 
rates on 30year fixedrate mortgages climbed from 1005 
percent at the start of april to 1058 percent at the end of may 
according to the federal home loan mortgage corp they eased 
slightly in the first weeks of june 
however some analysts had said the growing popularity of 
